high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the door, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the rightmost bottle of lotion off of the counter.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn around to face the counter.
Open the second lower drawer from the right and put the bottle of lotion inside, then close the drawer.
Walk up to the counter.
Pick up the bottle of lotion off of the counter.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn around to face the counter.
Open the second lower drawer from the right and put the bottle of lotion inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles of lotion into a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around to face the sink.
Pick up the rightmost bottle of lotion on the counter.
Turn to face the drawers under the sink.
Put the bottle of lotion away in the lower third drawer from the right.
Turn to face the bottle of lotion on the left on the counter.
Pick up the bottle of lotion.
Turn to face the drawers under the sink.
Put the other bottle of lotion away in the lower third drawer from the right.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles of lotion away in a drawer under the sink.

high_descs: Face the opposite direction and go to the door, then turn right and go to the countertop with two soap dispensers, under the mirror.
Pick up the soap dispenser on the right.
Pivot to your left, all the way around to face the counter again.
Put the soap dispenser into the bottom drawer, immediately to the left of the sink.
Move toward the counter, then back again.
Pick up the other soap dispenser from the counter to your left.
Pivot aimlessly left, all the way around once more.
Put the soap dispenser away in the bottom drawer, immediately left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two soap dispensers away in a bathroom drawer.
